  "text": "The remainder of the paper is organized as follows. In the next section we provide an overview of the key aspects of both the stochastic model by [CITATION_1] and a latent factor social network model, in a basketball setting. In section 3, we present our novel latent factor stochastic passing model in detail and discuss our parameter estimation procedure. Section 4 presents experimental results on synthetic datasets and real optical basketball tracking data, and lastly, the conclusion is in section 5.",
